{"tid":668824,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"獨愛足球員大脾 馮盈盈：夠粗好有力 一緊張就濕晒","createTime":"2018-05-18T03:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T12:44:39.000Z","uid":157545,"like":263,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1d09d8bba0f1b4a07e9ddf0f361a0edeaf65a2","tid":668824,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180517/photo/bkn-20180517165703303-0517_00862_001_05b.jpg?20180518052134\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180517%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180517165703303-0517_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20180518052134&h=bb496246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人馮盈盈於坑口出席「東港城 x captain tsubasa」球技格鬥場活動，以熱褲上陣的她，玩花式足球時不慎露出黑色打底褲！本身不踢波的她，覺得會踢足球的男仔特別吸引，更豪言喜歡男人腳粗有力，她說：「識踢波啲男仔會加分，覺得佢哋大髀會粗，夠晒力！咁樣我攰嗰陣，有時涼鞋斷咗帶都可以孭起我，抱起我！男友都玩曲棍球，試過打到塊面血管凸咗出嚟！（會阻止佢玩？）唔會，會做運動都係好事！」<br />\n<br />\n提到她當街攬實男友，她直言會經常翹實男友，因自己腰痛問題會易攰，依附在對方身上借力，笑指男友要盡做男友的責任。<br />\n<br />\n談到早前她在節目中，談起初戀拍拖時，會緊張到手濕，以「濕晒，地下都濕埋！」來形容，被網友指她豪放，她笑謂：「我有好明確咁講係隻手濕㗎，我一緊張就會濕，拖男仔手都會，愈唔諗就愈濕！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180517/photo/bkn-20180517165703303-0517_00862_001_04b.jpg?20180518052134\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180517%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180517165703303-0517_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20180518052134&h=3a6c0761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180517/photo/bkn-20180517165703303-0517_00862_001_03b.jpg?20180518052134\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180517%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180517165703303-0517_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20180518052134&h=0b743016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180517/photo/bkn-20180517165703303-0517_00862_001_02b.jpg?20180518052134\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.